{"tid":1053933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"HK01你好野","createTime":"2019-03-09T12:50:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T13:06:26.000Z","uid":190817,"like":632,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"84aeb27f623fc0d10c78c00773c3e7a23cebb1ff","tid":1053933,"uid":190817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T12:50:02.000Z","msg":"話說琴日出左個post<br />\n無意中發現香港郵局一早定義左公屋仔 居屋仔 私樓仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1052318/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1052318/page/1</a><br />\n估唔到大家咁熱烈討論 之後都預左HK01黎抄文<br />\n<br />\n果然不出所料抄文 仲要一出出三篇<br />\n<strong>郵政神級創意劃分香港38類人 一文睇晒你屬於哪個階級<br />\n【人有貴賤】郵政將港人分12 組38類 你係成就之巔定比下有餘？<br />\n郵政獨創38種港人分類法 多區無故被「降呢」居民嬲爆<br />\n</strong><br />\n中間都講左抄還抄落番個名<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w4Ogpx6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw4Ogpx6.png&h=a5c9376f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇第一篇岩岩發現果然有抄 不過呢就 <br />\n叫你落個名 你就同我寫連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第二篇無驚喜抄抄貼貼 唔講了<br />\n到第三篇我睇到噴飯<br />\n琴日有巴打講左肯定有傻仔話歧視<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cSVB8ZM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcSVB8ZM.png&h=1f7dcc51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點知你個記者就今日即刻訪問社區主任問係咪歧視<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過篇文都睇到社區主任自已都歧視啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n在分類當中，不少住宅和屋苑都被點名列入分類。如良景邨住戶被評為「H26邁向中年」，屬<span style=\"color: red;\">低收入、普遍教育程度較低，多從事建造業、運輸業、及倉務藍領工作</span>。<br />\n<br />\n良景社區主任王德源亦在網上對此表達關注，他向《香港01》稱分類標籤未能反映事實，「邨內有來自不同收入背景的人」，又指明白香港郵政作為財政獨立機構可為商戶提供特定服務，但分類「<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">難以令人觀感不太好，亦有不少街坊覺得被歧視</span></strong>」，認為郵政做法「多此一舉」，應交由客戶自行判斷挑選客戶。"},{"pid":"80390cd96a11ced9b92cb5c596d33bcccb280ee0","tid":1053933,"uid":190817,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T12:53:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7db3878afabc90e035890403d8fbcc3aed0aa451","tid":1053933,"uid":58358,"like":312,"dislike":2,"score":310,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T12:59:57.000Z","msg":"垃圾01"},{"pid":"d635f0c0b1e775fe5db402df59fd96a797ae52b9","tid":1053933,"uid":48083,"like":421,"dislike":4,"score":417,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T13:03:24.000Z","msg":"炒完人唔夠人手<br />\n一單料用三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"502f3a363e5502662cdaf087b031296d3efcc40a","tid":1053933,"uid":190817,"like":71,"dislike":5,"score":66,"quote":{"pid":"d635f0c0b1e775fe5db402df59fd96a797ae52b9","tid":1053933,"uid":48083,"like":421,"dislike":4,"score":417,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T13:03:24.000Z","msg":"炒完人唔夠人手<br />\n一單料用三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T13:03:50.000Z","msg":"似各自各做"},{"pid":"391398b6853e4a53fdfd9e678665988d1f0cf62a","tid":1053933,"uid":76747,"like":71,"dislike":5,"score":66,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T13:06:32.000Z","msg":"呢間野炒IT9<br />\n決定del app<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dc7f48e19e8e0d49a3437644118d2c3be9dc815","tid":1053933,"uid":47238,"like":10,"dislike":322,"score":-312,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T13:10:47.000Z","msg":"非打手，但其實有冇諗過，全世界任何地方傳媒，都一樣上網炒，呢個世代資訊係晒網上，唔抄邊有野做<br />\n至於落唔落名，老實說，落既啲人一樣嘈被擺上枱，唔落又嘈偷野，計落唔著好處多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然，大事例外，要負責既幾大都落"},{"pid":"d4ec7bfc921fc6c38163dfdbb4b51e6553155e64","tid":1053933,"uid":4942,"like":220,"dislike":2,"score":218,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T13:13:35.000Z","msg":"01 剩係識網上抄料 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\